## What I Need to Improve

**Written Communication**

While my spoken communication improved this week, my written notes and code comments still needed more detail. Sometimes I left out important information, which made it harder for teammates to follow my work without asking me questions.

Areas to work on:
- Writing more complete code comments
- Including enough context in task notes so others can understand without asking
- Being more consistent with the level of detail in documentation

