## Reflection

This week helped me realise that communication is not just about talking — writing clearly is just as important in a team environment. When my notes are incomplete, it creates extra work for my teammates because they have to come back and ask me questions. I want to build a habit of writing good notes from the start so that my work is easy for anyone to pick up and understand.

